translation[4]{c,v,t}:
  5,14,"Nakwabo bazibiza ngokuba bangamaKhristu, Sathabatha uMnqophiso kubo kodwa sele betyeshele isahlulo esikhulu soMyalezo owawuthunyelwe kubo. Ke kaloku Sahlwayela ubutshaba nenzondwano phakathi kwabo, kude kube yiMini yoVuko, kwaye uAllâh Uza kubazisa abakwenzayo"
  5,15,Hini na nina Bantu beNcwadi! Ngoku ufikile uMprofeti weThu kuni (uMuhammad) enicacisela okuninzi enanikufihla esiBhalweni nikuqakatha ngamandla. Inene ukukhanya kufikile kuni kuvela kuAllâh neNcwadi ecacileyo (i’Kur’ân)
  5,16,"UAllâh Ukhokela ngayo bonke abakwiNtando yaKhe, abalandela iindlela zoxolo, Aze kananjalo Abakhuphe ebumnyameni ngeNtando yaKhe, Abakhokelele ekukhanyeni nakwiNdlela ethe Tye"
  5,17,"Inene, abangakholwanga ngabo bathi uAllâh nguMesiya, unyana kaMariyam. Yithi wena (Muhammad): “Ngubani na ngoko onentwana yamandla okuchasana noAllâh ukuba Ebenokusuka amtshabalalise uMesiya, unyana kaMaryam, nomama wakhe, nabo bonke abo basemhlabeni? Yaye loluka-Allâh ulongamelo lwamazulu nomhlaba nako konke okuphakathi kwawo. Udala oko Athande ukukudala kwaye uAllâh Uyakwazi ukwenza izinto zonke"